Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯像管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果失敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍吧！
