Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱作「天使的階梯」的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理就好像正在被那光芒吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像這樣下去 真由理就會消失一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你被帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理是我的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是人體實驗的樣品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫口而出的 是小時候學會的那些臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真由理一起看的一部電視劇中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學狂人像瘋子一樣喊出的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫的人質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說在打瞌睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快五點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去訂披薩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別點熱帶水果特製披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間跳躍 成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剛剛去邀請琉華氏參加Party了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發評議會中止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止？ 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都趕快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了！ 快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎！ 一定要回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是接了一下手機嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕 這裡是真由喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在無法接聽電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子世界線並沒有發生巨大改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和發送D-MAIL的時候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是真的回到了今天5點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喀嗒喀嗒 新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧 新幹線是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後 真由理會帶著鈴羽回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該去報警嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 誰會相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未來時間跳躍回來這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剩下的三小時內必須得做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理！ 真由理！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…不 凶真…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？ 什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概30分鐘之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是回Lab去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她還沒回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她特地來邀請我去參加Party
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我今天實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有說會順路去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理醬嗎？ 沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到她的話 立刻打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然世界線沒有變化 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理自身的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不去影響是不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵 菲利斯現在不能接電話喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理你到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不說過今天解散了嗎 你快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是從未來時間跳躍回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你從接手機的那一瞬間起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像整個人都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這樣子 應該是發生了什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒時間跟你詳細說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你先逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃？ 逃去哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪都行 盡可能遠離Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要好好解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 也替我轉告桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部倫太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 泡茶的水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到過真由理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名真由理？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才正好在邀請我去參加Party呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡右轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 泡茶的水到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綯想去買東西 我得送她過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問路的話去派出所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 送她過去後你也別回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是一番星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ Party呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跟克莉絲和桶子說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我都邀請鈴小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有桶子君也訂了披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 照我說的做！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你經常做一些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天的你是真的莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想進行實驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在能照我說的做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會跟你詳細說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜只是有點吃驚罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這時候是回家的尖峰期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 但是大廳裡一個人都沒有哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.44,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再通知一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.52,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於出現了爆炸預告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.57,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫時停止行駛的路線如下所示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.71,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.5\fs29\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(431,288)}由於出現了爆炸的恐怖預告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.71,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.7\fs29\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(580,393)}現在警視廳鐵路警察正在調查可疑物品，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.71,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.7\fs29\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(703,390)}以下所有路線暫時停駛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說還沒有恢復行駛的跡象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 討厭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會犯這種低級錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地鐵 快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岡部倫太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的呆呆站著幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來 拼命跑起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的是椎名真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 岡部倫太郎被捕獲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理 我一定會救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止？ 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了今晚Mr.顯像管會來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫 你又搞出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真由理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟真由理說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之留在這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太硬來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算可疑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓大家遠離Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕 這裡是真由喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都會很花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就跟剛才一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得做點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉華子 是我 岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凶真先…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在你那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理醬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 她現在正想回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我叫住她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我過來之前 絕對不要讓她離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她說要回Lab…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 照我說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理醬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嗒哢嗒 新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧 新幹線是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 岡倫 嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正準備修補好吹雪醬的COS服就回Lab呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹雪醬？ 是一起COSPLAY的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她說真由喜做的COS服的線頭散了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛收到了簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等修補好了 馬上就回Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能趕上Party的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 Party…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Lab暫時無法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我希望你能陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹雪醬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不過這事得先放著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十萬火急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…發生什麼事了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 接下來我們要出趟遠門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎？ 就你們兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吹雪醬那邊明天也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快沒時間搭電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真由喜什麼都沒準備啊 錢也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些你不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原車站不是在對面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭地鐵走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很久沒有像這樣被岡倫拉著走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往回走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.35,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.5\bord0\be1\pos(832,100)}發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.35,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.5\bord0\be1\pos(487,294)}之後要給我說明清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 真由喜的懷錶停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 明明才剛上過發條
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人還真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總武線停止行駛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止行駛了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是接到電話 說有人安裝了炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜雖然有一肚子疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在會忍住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過作為交換
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一切都結束的時候 希望你能告訴我全部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能幫上你的忙 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party…以後再開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後…一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是想…給姐姐一個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會讓你死…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…我…一定會救你的！

Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:27.98,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}規制された視界 無慈悲なる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:36.74,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十二の支配 逃れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:45.16,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安息の明日を願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:54.30,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手の中の尊い事象の地平へ
